# Coalesce automation, AI-assistant, and tooling authorship to the maintainer
# so the GitHub contributor graph reflects the human author. No bot or AI
# assistant should appear as a separate contributor.
#
# Format (note the order): Proper-Name <proper-email> <commit-email>
# i.e. the LEFT identity is the canonical one; the RIGHT email is the one
# rewritten onto it. The previous version had this reversed and relabelled the
# maintainer's own commits as "Claude".

